text: Cratena minor is a species of sea slug, an aeolid nudibranch, a marine gastropod mollusc in the family Facelinidae.MolluscaBase (2018). Cratena minor Padula, Araújo, Matthews-Cascon & Schrödl, 2014. Accessed on 2018-02-17. ==Distribution== This species was described from Brazil. ==References== Category:Facelinidae Category:Gastropods described in 2014
title: Cratena minor
